name: Pet Feeding Mats - Smiley
description:
Minimize mess during meals for your furry family. These personalized pet feeding mats come in playful bone (2x sizes) and whimsical fish (1x size) shapes. A non-slip bottom keeps them in place, and a foam-filled material is highly absorbent.

NB: Print colors may not soak through due to fabric thickness, and white background may show through when stroked.

.: Material: 100% polyester outer layer, 100% polyurethane memory foam core
.: Anti-slip backing
.: One-sided print
.: Pre-constructed item (size varies ±1”)
